# Adsomnia Chat Interface Design Guidelines

## Brand Identity
Adsomnia is a high-energy affiliate marketing and traffic platform. The brand exudes confidence, operates 24/7 ("Traffic Never Sleeps"), and communicates with bold, direct visual language.

